Exception - Class

Exception = Its like a run time error, when it happens in our code, the remaining lines of code will
not be processed.

Why should i handle the exception?

Inorder the process the entire piece of code

To know where the exception happened and reason

How to handle the exception ?

Using Try-Catch block.

Who is super class in Java?

"OBJECT"

